CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 12, 1959, pg. A2 reads: "First Day - Counting parochial schools, 370,000 pupils were back in school Tuesday. Attending for the first time, were, left, students at Cresson...-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group of children, including young boy wearing Niagara Falls t-shirt, standing outside of open double doors of Cresson school for first day of class
